sequenceDiagram
  participant CLI as CLI handler
  participant ID as Shared identity
  participant WEB as Web handler

  CLI->>ID: create identity
  CLI->>ID: create invite
  WEB->>ID: join via invite
  CLI->>ID: set profile text
  ID-->>WEB: replicate profile update
  WEB->>ID: set avatar
  ID-->>CLI: replicate avatar update
